{"tid":2350762,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"滙豐指許智峯相關信用卡事宜應向執法機構查詢 滙豐不能評論相關帳戶的事情","createTime":"2021-01-02T14:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T16:24:34.000Z","uid":291865,"like":2,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ed8212918baf008c192510c363a44c24346948b4","tid":2350762,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T14:46:46.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】流亡到英國的許智峯說，他和家人的滙豐信用卡在沒有被通知下全部遭取消。<br />\n<br />\n許智峯在社交網站指，他和家人的滙豐信用卡由於消費退款關係，餘額有約數萬港元，他引述滙豐銀行指，餘款未必可獲退回，銀行又解釋取消他們信用卡是商業決定。<br />\n<br />\n許智峯指批評滙豐的決定完全無法律基礎，質疑商界在國安法下依附及順從政權，要求滙豐公開交代並促請監管機構調查，否則會考慮其他國際上的跟進行動。<br />\n<br />\n滙豐回應表示不能評論相關帳戶的事情，無論在哪個市場營運都必須符合當地的法律法規，有關個案的情況，請向執法機構查詢。"},{"pid":"0c0e4b2cc57d461b6401cbabe214baa3f73af376","tid":2350762,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T14:46:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=418785\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D418785&d=%2Bt7hcjB4BRnTGQ5b2LOb0xYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=8ac35f1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D418785&h=7a0efe30\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=418785</a>"},{"pid":"102b0435a66ceb226a99ecd920e1382b6f1104f8","tid":2350762,"uid":239270,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T14:48:38.000Z","msg":"執法機構指應向匯豐查詢"},{"pid":"63013b3e1c50361fead3306a1fba4c2293ad923d","tid":2350762,"uid":77880,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T14:49:16.000Z","msg":"唔問銀行，去問執法機關？"},{"pid":"1e6fa35e6cf7f71c99b12b26eba30c546604b80a","tid":2350762,"uid":113000,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T14:49:19.000Z","msg":"十分黑警口吻<br />\n<br />\n有咩去投訴科投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7029659dcf6e08c24660adfdccede04cbb83fc","tid":2350762,"uid":33890,"like